OWAKE waba yiphini likasihlalo we-ANC eTshwane, uMnuz Mapiti Matsena ugwazwe washona wumsolwa ongaziwa ebusuku ngoLwesithathu esendlini yakhe eDoornpoort. UMatsena, 54, ubesewusihlalo ekomidini lezokuphepha komphakathi esiShayamthetho saseGauteng. Ngokwesitatimende samaphoyisa aseSinoville, abizwe emzini kaMatshena ngezithuba zawo 10.52pm. "Uma befika bazithele phezu kwesidumbu sikamufi phansi endlini yakhe yokulala. Kubizwe abezimo eziphuthumayo kodwa imizamo yabo igcine ihlulekile,"kusho isitatimende. Amaphoyisa aphinde abika ukuthi uMatsena wehlelwa yilo mshophi nje ubevuke eya endlini encane, wazithela phezu kombulali wakhe ongene ngewindi lengilazi ebelingavaliwe. "Umsolwa uqale wamboza unkosikazi kamufi ngengubo yokulala". "Unkosikazi kamufi ukwazile ukuphuma wayobiza indodana yabo uMokwele Matsena kwenye indlu ofikile naye wazibonela impi ebe khona ngaphambi kokuthi uyise agwazwe esifubeni". Namhlanje ekuseni amazwi endunduzo abelokhu engene njalo kulo mndeni njengoba izindaba zokudlula emhlabeni kukaMatsena bese zigcwele nasezinkundleni zokuxhumana. Usechazwe njengomuntu obethanda abantu futhi obesebenza ngokuzikhandla ukuze kusizakala umphakathi. 